What Factors Will Affect Your Housing Price¶

I am really interested in real estate market and always interested what causing the housing price.

*) Picture took from https://www.newamericanfunding.com/mortgage-real-estate-trends/home-prices-rising-every-major-housing-market/

Business Understanding¶

I did analysis using the dataset(AmesHouring.csv) I found from Kaggle. And I found the answers to the following questions:

  1. How factors are correlated to each other?
  2. What are the factors which affects the housing price mostly?
  3. Is the result be intuitively verified?

Build Linear Regression Model¶

Build the linear regression model and get the coef and intercept

In [45]:
#Linear Regression Modeling
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression
lr = LinearRegression(fit_intercept=True)
df = df.fillna(0)
trainx = df[coln]
trainx = (trainx-trainx.mean())/trainx.std()
trainy = df['SalePrice']

lr.fit(trainx.values,trainy.values)
lr.coef_
lr.intercept_
Out[45]:
180796.06006825942

Draw the graph to show the difference¶

trainy value is in red and estimated value in green

In [46]:
#Visualization and check the difference
plt.figure(figsize=(15,7))
plt.plot(np.arange(300), trainy[:300], c='red', linestyle=None)
plt.plot(np.arange(300), np.dot(lr.coef_, trainx[:300].T)+lr.intercept_, c='green', linestyle='--')
